Dane, Greg: Proceed with the deployment using these credentials. I am documenting this as an 'emergency necessity' to mitigate irreparable harm to the company and to maintain our fiduciary obligations. We will provide the SEC with a full, transparent accounting of this process post-incident. Speed is now our only path to compliance.

